 basic computer, programming and probability theory background is required.</li>\n<li>The course site contains links to the lecture videos, reading material and assignments.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2020-11-29T17:45:50.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"EbookFoundation/free-programming-books","categoryHTML":"<h4>Pandas</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://pandas.pydata.org/docs/pandas.pdf\">pandas: powerful Python data analysis toolkit</a> - Wes McKinney and the Pandas Development Team (🚧 <em>in process</em>) (PDF)</li>","updatedAt":"2020-11-29T17:27:04.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"homematic-community/awesome-homematic","categoryHTML":"<h2>CCU Addons</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/thkl/hap-homematic\">HAP-HomeMatic</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/thkl/hap-homematic\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">125</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":125,\"repo\":\"thkl/hap-homematic\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - RaspberryMatic / CCU3 addon to access your HomeMatic devices from HomeKit. Its much like <a href=\"https://github.com/thkl/homebridge-homematic\">https://github.com/thkl/homebridge-homematic</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/thkl/homebridge-homematic\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;b